<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="爱家理财">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" id="viewport">
    <title>旅行分期费率说明</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/kmjr.app.base.css?v=20151019" />
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../../lib/jquery/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="dialog">
    <div class="dialog-explain">
            <div class="dialog-content">
                <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" class="dialog-table">
                    <tr>
                        <td width="10%" rowspan="4" class="text-align-c">旅行分期</td>
                        <td width="30%">还款方式</td>
                        <td width="60%">计算公式</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>正常还款</td>
                        <td style="padding: 0; border-width: 0;" >
                            <table  cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" width="100%" style="border: 0;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td colspan="2">每期应还款＝借款总金额 /分期期数＋借款总金额* 每期费率</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>分期期限</td>
                                    <td>每期费率（含利息及服务费）</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>3个月</td>
                                    <td>1%</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>6个月</td>
                                    <td>0.9%</td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                          </td>
                      </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>提前一次性还清款项</td>
                        <td>提前一次性还清款项=原剩余应还总金额-（剩余应还利息＋服务费）*50%</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>逾期</td>
                        <td>逾期违约金＝当期剩余应还金额*1%*逾期天数</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
    </div>
<script>
    $('.dialog-table').css({'width':window.innerWidth+'px'})
</script>
